*Govorio* sam joj da mora da se spremi. (I told her she had to get ready.)

*Govorili* smo o njenom planu. (We talked about her plan.)

Moj otac je *govorio* o stvarima koje nisam razumela. (My father was talking about things I didn't understand.)

Moja sestra *govorila* je o bitnim temama. (My sister was talking about important topics.)

On je *govorio* da je bio u pravu. (He was saying that he was right.)

